I'll get through to her.

00:10.160 --> 00:12.891
TOMMY: <i>The union convenor causing all
the trouble. Her name's jessie Eden.</i>

00:12.960 --> 00:15.088
I will conduct myself as a businessman.

00:15.160 --> 00:16.571
Who says sweetheart.

00:16.640 --> 00:20.406
Today, everyone in the family
received one of these.

00:20.480 --> 00:22.767
TOMMY: <i>Changretta knows where we all
live. We need to be together in a place</i>

00:22.840 --> 00:24.490
<i>even they won't dare to come.</i>

00:24.560 --> 00:25.971
<i>ADA". You mean back home?</i>

00:26.040 --> 00:28.008
<i>MICHAEL: This is the New York Mafia
we 're talking about!</i>

00:28.080 --> 00:29.764
<i>JO</i> H N: <i>Ana' we 're the Peaky Blinders!</i>

00:29.840 --> 00:32.286
<i>MXCHAEL". We're not the Peaky Blinders
unless we're together.</i>

00:32.360 --> 00:34.362
- What's the purpose of your visit?
- Pleasure.

