56:03.000 --> 56:04.570
What, the shithouse?

56:06.040 --> 56:10.090
No. I don't know what it is.

56:11.280 --> 56:14.648
Birmingham, I suppose. Small Heath.

56:16.360 --> 56:19.682
- That smell.
