Well, he's gone, though.

56:28.560 --> 56:30.289
Like a hole behind your head.

56:32.640 --> 56:34.722
Thought you thought
there was are heaven.

56:35.240 --> 56:39.006
No. More like hell for ourjohn.

56:40.440 --> 56:41.930
No, neither one.

56:44.160 --> 56:45.924
He's just not here anymore.

